  "title": "Livestream Host (Shopee Live & TikTok Shop)",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Host live product sessions on Shopee Live & TikTok Shop</p></li><li><p>Interact with viewers and answer live questions</p></li><li><p>Co-host livestreams with company guests</p></li><li><p>Follow livestream scripts and training guidelines</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Confident, well-spoken, and comfortable on camera</p></li><li><p>Positive, friendly, and energetic personality</p></li><li><p>Able to work weekends</p></li><li><p>Prior livestream or sales experience is a plus but not required</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Training & Benefits</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Paid training at <strong>$10/hour</strong></p></li><li><p>Full livestream training provided in Singapore 🇸🇬</p></li><li><p>Opportunity to gain experience in e-commerce and live selling</p></li></ul><p>📥 <strong>Application Instructions:</strong><br />Please apply via MyCareersFuture.<br />Optional: Attach a short intro video to stand out.</p>",
